ote><br />\n聽講長線勁過700 ，我沽左700 買992</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n992真係唔敢再買，但當佢係中國蘋果又好似搏得過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知連登係咪好多巴打有貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多po都有人推992<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">聯想集團(<a href=\"http://00992.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00992.HK&d=I5rhD1x2HRYd34zFQG3l%2B57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=aada834e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00992.HK</a>)自首季盈轉蝕7,200萬美元後，遭多間外資行唱淡，瑞銀今天更降其目標價至3元，預計市場將下調預測。該股連續第三天尋底，今早逆市低見4.28元，創六年低，現造4.31元，續跌2.9%，成交4,819萬股。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">摩通</span>昨天指，聯想集團個人電腦利潤表現差，加上移動及數據中心業務持續虧損，導致上季繼續錄得經營虧損，預期未來個人電腦業務因應零件成本增加令利潤持續受壓，移動業務也會因競爭加劇扭虧機會降，數據中心轉勢計劃仍於初期階段，預期其未來18個月維持虧損，加上毛利維持疲弱，故下調公司2018-19年每股盈測期，目標價也由4.2元降至<span style=\"color: red;\">4</span>元。此外，<span style=\"color: red;\">花旗</span>料聯想集團數據中心業務或需兩年才可達至收支平衡，故將其2018、2019及2020財年盈測分別下調23%/7%/2%，並維持「沽售」評級，看<span style=\"color: red;\">3.2</span>元。<span style=\"color: red;\">美銀美林</span>績後也降聯想集團盈測，目標價削至<span style=\"color: red;\">3.6</span>元。</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E8%81%AF%E6%83%B3%E9%9B%86%E5%9C%98-00992-hk-%E7%BA%8C%E8%B7%8C3-%E5%89%B5%E5%85%AD%E5%B9%B4%E4%BD%8E-031300585.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E8%2581%25AF%25E6%2583%25B3%25E9%259B%2586%25E5%259C%2598-00992-hk-%25E7%25BA%258C%25E8%25B7%258C3-%25E5%2589%25B5%25E5%2585%25AD%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E4%25BD%258E-031300585.html&d=I5rhD1x2HRYd34zFQG3l%2B57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=9ea948b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yaho